'''苏巴卡卡'''（{{lang-hi|सुभाष काक}}，Subhash Kak，{{bd|1947年|3月26日}}）是[[美国|美国]]籍[[印度|印度]][[计算机科学|计算机科学]]家<ref>{{Cite book|title=A place at the multicultural table the development of an American Hinduism|url=https://archive.org/details/placeatmulticult00kuri|author=Kurien, Prema A.|date=2007|publisher=Rutgers University Press|isbn=9780813540559|pages=[https://archive.org/details/placeatmulticult00kuri/page/n178 163], 166|oclc=703221465}}</ref>，出生于[[斯利那加|斯利那加]]。现为[[俄克拉何马州立大学静水校区|俄克拉何马州立大学静水校区]]资深教授<ref name="Hindu">{{cite news|url=https://www.thehindu.com/features/magazine/the-renaissance-man/article5478590.ece|title=The Renaissance man|first=Usha|last=Akella|date=21 December 2013|access-date=2 December 2018|newspaper=The Hindu}}</ref>、[[賈瓦哈拉爾·尼赫魯大學|賈瓦哈拉爾·尼赫魯大學]]客座教授<ref name="jnu.ac.in">https://www.jnu.ac.in/se-faculty</ref>，印度总理科学、技术与创新咨询委员会（PM-STIAC）成员<ref name="thehindubusinessline.com">{{cite web|url=https://www.thehindubusinessline.com/news/new-committee-formed-to-advise-pm-on-science-tech-related-policy-matters/article24799809.ece|title=New committee formed to advise PM on science, tech-related policy issues|website=Thehindubusinessline.com|access-date=2 December 2018}}</ref>。

卡卡发表过有关[[科学史|科学史]]，[[科学哲学|科学哲学]]，[[天文学史|天文学史]]、[[数学史|数学史]]的论文，卡卡还发表过关于[[考古天文学|考古天文学]]的文章，并提倡土著雅利安人（{{le|Indigenous Aryans}}）的思想。但其理论被其他许多学者批评。{{sfn|Witzel|2001}}<ref name=":1">{{Cite journal|last=Guha|first=Sudeshna|date=2007|title=Review of The Indo-Aryan Controversy: Evidence and Inference in Indian History|journal=Journal of the Royal Asiatic Society|volume=17|issue=3|pages=340–343|issn=1356-1863|jstor=25188742|doi=10.1017/S135618630700733X}}</ref>

2019年被印度政府授予[[莲花士勋章|莲花士勋章]]。<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.ddinews.gov.in/national/padma-awards-conferred-president-ram-nath-kovind|title=Padma Awards conferred by President Ram Nath Kovind {{!}} DD News|website=www.ddinews.gov.in|access-date=2019-03-23}}</ref>

